description	"Han Solo

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (2)

^8Attributes:
- Healing (3)

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS1]
- Gun Kick ^3[CS3]

After only just being freed from the carbonite, Han was quickly swooped off to the pit of carkoon whilst still under the side-effects of staying in carbonite.
On the trip to the Pit, his vision improved so much that he could "see a light blur instead of a dark blur", Luke promptly reminded him there was nothing to see on tatooine anyway.
Han Solo has stolen a pistol from one of the guards and is now using to kill Jabba's hencemen"